{"tid":1512022,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來放低真係咁難","createTime":"2019-08-27T17:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T16:48:35.000Z","uid":38799,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"845dbca5ef2082d98b55dbe2df9ff143516e36ba","tid":1512022,"uid":38799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:10:18.000Z","msg":"自問係個拎得起放得低既男人<br />\n直至上一個...<br />\n未試過咁掛念一個人<br />\n過幾日就係我地當年正式一齊既日子<br />\n真係好想搵番佢<br />\n但我知佢已經唔再想理會我<br />\n依一年發夢又見到佢聽歌又諗起佢<br />\n好辛苦 放低幾時變到咁難<br />\n我地應承要再睇多次星空<br />\n我地話過唔會離開對方<br />\n唔知佢有冇諗起我"},{"pid":"3b3690a421bd230f6441aa1b4309cf392a01acfd","tid":1512022,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:11:39.000Z","msg":"香港就收皮啦仲掛住放低"},{"pid":"a79a1b377ad3714507ef24a5fd526c9ecdebdefe","tid":1512022,"uid":62167,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:23:56.000Z","msg":"時間會沖淡一切<br />\nbtw<br />\n被愛很幸福 愛人很痛苦"},{"pid":"636cb71cddfb8a6e433d2f27d5c98cd88bfc1a30","tid":1512022,"uid":234219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:27:42.000Z","msg":"放低一個人真係一件好難既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cfc063153f576bff4420166ea7386e11a23889e","tid":1512022,"uid":136252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:29:28.000Z","msg":"Same ，但可以只係心有不甘"},{"pid":"db01df34a336fbdf2e5cae4c2c49ed57763a7eb8","tid":1512022,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cfc063153f576bff4420166ea7386e11a23889e","tid":1512022,"uid":136252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:29:28.000Z","msg":"Same ，但可以只係心有不甘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:29:39.000Z","msg":"可能"},{"pid":"236f01c275b9486d7664bfaed506d40b49f5a056","tid":1512022,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:40:07.000Z","msg":"分手一年 淡左而分手<br />\n中間有識第二個 但最尾都係諗番佢<br />\n人真係好犯賤"},{"pid":"effa79976d781c2b5c8597410928161914437